{
  "$schema": "https://docs.renovatebot.com/renovate-schema.json",
  "description": "Usage: 'github>AmadeusITGroup/otter//tools/renovate/yarn2/sdk-spec-upgrade-with-auth(@my-company/spec-package, //npm.my-company.example/api/npm/npm/, NPM_AUTH_BASE64)' - Trigger SDK regeneration for a specific package name with Yarn Berry (Yarn >= 2), with private registry authentication. arg0: full package name. arg1: scheme-less registry URL with trailing slash (e.g. '//npm.my-company.example/api/npm/npm/'). arg2: name of the environment variable holding the base64-encoded 'user:password' token (e.g. 'NPM_AUTH_BASE64'); must be exposed to Renovate via customEnvVariables.",
  "extends": [
    "github>AmadeusITGroup/otter//tools/renovate/group/sdk-spec({{arg0}})",
    "github>AmadeusITGroup/otter//tools/renovate/yarn2/tasks/sdk-spec-regenerate-with-auth.json5({{arg0}}, {{arg1}}, {{arg2}})"
  ]
}
